    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Following Wang Puzi's research, xieshan zhuanjiao has the same meaning as xieshan, commonly translated as hip-gable roof. Indeed, xieshan may be short for xieshan zhuanjiao because they are used interchangeably (Wang 1995, 6-10).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
